show.title: Yama Ling
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/ASdru6
show.description: A boy becomes the target of a deadly conspiracy, but he narrowly escapes with his life. Seeking refuge in a distant mountain, he disappears from the world. Over the next ten years, he immerses himself in intense Tantric practices, purifying his body and soul to gain divine powers. Once awakened with mystical strength, he descends the mountain—returning to confront those who wronged him and to take revenge for the betrayal against him and his family. Watch "Yama Ling" now!
